mistral.reason: Donald Collins was not succeeded by Leo Kieffer. Instead, Leo Kieffer was the one who succeeded Don's father (Samuel W. Collins) in the family lumber business, S.W. Collins Co., and later sold it to Rob Kieffer in 1989.
